snippet.title: RunaWFE
snippet.description: RunaWFE is a workflow / BPM based on JBOSS JBPM and Activiti engines

snippet.title: Mondrian
snippet.description: Mondrian is an OLAP (online analytical processing) engine written in Java. It reads from JDBC data sources, aggregates data in a memory cache, and implements the MDX language and the olap4j and XML/A APIs.

snippet.title: XAMPP
snippet.description: XAMPP is a very easy to install Apache Distribution for Linux, Solaris, Windows and Mac OS X. The package includes the Apache web server, MySQL, PHP, Perl, a FTP server and phpMyAdmin.

snippet.title: MySQL
snippet.description: The world's most popular open source database.

snippet.title: HyperSQL Database Engine (HSQLDB)
snippet.description: HSQLDB is a relational database engine written in Java, with a JDBC driver, conforming to ANSI SQL:2008. A small, fast, multithreaded engine and server with memory and disk tables, LOBs, transaction isolation, multiversion concurrency and ACID.

snippet.title: PyTables - Hierarchical datasets
snippet.description: The goal of PyTables is to enable the end user to efficiently and easily manipulate large datasets (both homogenous, i.e. arrays, and heterogenous, i.e. tables) on a persistent, hierarchical way.

snippet.title: jWorld
snippet.description: Virtual reality simulation (Java) with physics engines (JNI)

snippet.title: The Lemur Project
snippet.description: The Lemur Project develops search engines, browser toolbars, text analysis tools, and data resources that support research and development of information retrieval and text mining software, including the Indri search engine and ClueWeb09 dataset.

snippet.title: AWStats
snippet.description: AWStats is a free powerful and featureful server logfile analyzer that shows you all your Web/Mail/FTP statistics including visits, unique visitors, pages, hits, rush hours, os, browsers, search engines, keywords, robots visits, broken links and more

snippet.title: Firebird
snippet.description: Firebird is a powerful cross platform SQL database system
